race.comment: ALLAN KEEPING (6) rocketed around the Wentworth Park 520m in 29.37 for a 5.5 lengths victory last time. Top win latest and looms as the one to beat again. O'KEEFE (1) was a sharp 19.84 winner of a Grade 5 at Goulburn last start. Top win latest and rates a key player again. ROBERT KEEPING (7) looks close to another win after finishing third from Box 1 last time (29.85) at Wentworth Park. Expected to be in the finish again. ESME WATSON (2) is a last-start placegetter here at this trip - worth considering.
